       Gremlin saw Darkfates blast and rolled away. He eyes the curiously odd 
bot, and then sent two large missles wizzing at hom. Then, he returned to 
Drillbit.

       The armor on Jackle's back sent the feather knife sliding away. Jackle 
turned, and fired at Blacknightmares face, then wnet back to Drillbit.

       Pheniox ducked from Scorpyo's shots, but was hit in her left wing. She 
shook it off and watched as a few trees began to fall. She sent some 
fireballs at him.
